data.description: This charming property boasts three spacious bedrooms and two full bathrooms, providing ample living space for a family. Step into the fully fenced backyard, enclosed by a privacy fence, offering a serene oasis perfect for outdoor activities and relaxation. The kitchen has granite countertops and sleek stainless steel appliances. The open first floor layout creates a welcoming and interconnected living space, where you can seamlessly move from the kitchen to the dining and living areas. This home combines comfort, style, and functionality, making it an ideal choice for those seeking a comfortable and inviting place to call home.
